ashok kumar (born 20 july 1983) is a professional golfer from india, currently playing on the professional golf tour of india, where he was the 2003/04 and the 2006/07 order of merit winner. kumar was born in bihar in 1983 and turned professional in 2002. in 2004, he won the hero honda golf tour order of merit for the 2003/04 season. he won it again in 2006/07 under the name of the pgti after recording 5 wins in 8 events played, where he finished in the top-10 in all 8 of them. kumar played in 12 events in 2008, but did not record a win, finishing in the top-10 8 times. kumar added another win in 2009 in april at the all india match play championship